snippet.title: TAS Zero no Tsukaima Fantasy Force (PS2)
snippet.description:
After too many hours wrestling with PCSX2-rr I finally was able to get this finished.  Apologies for the lack of pixel perfect video, PSCX2-rr's .avi recording wasn't playing nice and I had to use Nvidia shadowplay + fullscreen to get this recorded, which obviously introduces upscaling artifacts


This is my first TAS and there's still plenty that could be improved on before uploading it to TASVideos or WorldOfLongplays, I might go back and improve it in the future -


Feel free to ask me any questions in the comment section


You can also contact me on Twitter -
https://twitter.com/Kirby0Louise
